## First run: 2 failures (NavSmokeTest)
#   StandardTestDispatcher -> navigated screen's VM init/loadFor scheduled AFTER advanceUntilIdle;
#   list/detail stuck in Loading -> PLANT_LIST/"Pasi" not displayed.
#   FIX: Dispatchers.setMain(UnconfinedTestDispatcher()) -> eager inline; non-suspending fakes settle
#   state synchronously; idle() = composeRule.waitForIdle(). Deterministic, no production change.
# Also added @OptIn(ExperimentalCoroutinesApi) to silence UnconfinedTestDispatcher opt-in warnings.

